{"tid":376783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係五光十色呀！","createTime":"2017-08-27T08:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T08:58:18.000Z","uid":7033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72281fa2a09bf527fd6efdebf9043b253a7ddd87","tid":376783,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"澳門消息：下周國際煙花匯演取消<br />\n08月26日(六) 19:20  <br />\n<br />\n今年的澳門國際煙花比賽匯演取消。(資料圖片)<br />\n澳門風災後全城悲慟，澳門政府宣布，即日(26日)起取消近期一系列公眾、節慶、文娛康體及交流活動，包括第29屆澳門國際煙花比賽匯演及相關活動，以集中資源和力量，處理颱風「天鴿」的善後工作。 <br />\n<br />\n一年一度的澳門國際煙花比賽匯演，原定今年9月2日至10月1日分5個周末或周日舉行，5天活動合共有10場煙花表演，今年10支比賽隊伍分別來自澳洲、奧地利、英國、法國、日本、菲律賓、德國、意大利、葡萄牙和中國。 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/mobile/bkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170826%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html&d=ABAp%2BiCMwl6VFSawRmSdZZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d1b43d38\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170826/mobile/bkn-20170826192019585-0826_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"afb057f1b14e8e80238f665d02950c3a02dc83c0","tid":376783,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:53:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba1caf6c42af0f486a06c8f33e59076b0e405e74","tid":376783,"uid":7033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T08:58:18.000Z","msg":"唔洗再睇個洗腦廣告啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}